rComments: I have NEVER had to work so hard in an introductory course. The workload is absolutely ridiculous : online assignments every week (2-4hrs), readings every week (2-3hrs), mid-term essay (5-6 pages), mid-term, final, final essay (8-10 pages). The same class in English : 3 book reports (2-3 pages), multiple choice midterm and final, half the readings

rComments: Hardest class I've ever taken. Spoke to 3rd years who had a different prof. They said the textbook was supposed to be used over two courses, not one like she did. As soon as there's a lesson presented, you don't have time to learn it and there's a new one.

Really hard class. Have to show up, intense participation is mandatory,very grammar based. She gives great feedback and will help immensely during her office hours. Funny and very nice, shame the subject isn't interesting to me.

Awesome lady! Great professor! She knows her Latin, and is passionate about teaching it.
